sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Student / Graduate
    participant Login as Registration / Login Interface
    participant Auth as Authentication Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Dash as User Dashboard
    participant Resume as Resume Upload Module
    participant NLP as NLP Processing Module
    participant Rec as Recommendation Engine
    participant Coach as AI Coach

    U->>Login: Register / Login
    Login->>Auth: Submit credentials
    Auth->>DB: Verify / create user
    DB-->>Auth: Session established
    Auth-->>Dash: Redirect to dashboard
    Dash-->>U: Show personalized feed

    U->>Resume: Upload resume
    Resume->>NLP: Parse & analyze
    NLP->>Rec: Extracted skills & experience
    Rec->>DB: Store match scores
    Rec-->>Dash: Updated recommendations
    Dash-->>U: Show jobs, score, skill gaps

    U->>Coach: Ask career question
    Coach->>Rec: Fetch profile context
    Rec-->>Coach: Relevant data
    Coach-->>U: Personalized guidance
